        <title>可笑的人类造物（1）- 常见社交模式</title>
        <link>https://aruCUMA.github.io/p/%E5%8F%AF%E7%AC%91%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E7%B1%BB%E9%80%A0%E7%89%A91-%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E7%A4%BE%E4%BA%A4%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F/</link>
